# base-app

This is a starter app for a single page application. It's based on 
**Nextjs** (https://github.com/zeit/next.js/) and integrates the basic 
essential features to start working on it. 

- Serving **Nextjs** app over express server (Only for local development)
- Parametrized routing (with example)
- Serving static files under /static
- Exports Serverless handler (GCF)
- Include styled-jsx by default (You can later decide for a different tool)
- No Flux library included. (Up to you)
- No tests integrated (Up to you)
